nt/uploads/2016/09/Tap-OPEN-atau-SEND-Enjoy-as..-1.jpg?fit=640%2C536\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2358 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Tap-OPEN-atau-SEND-Enjoy-as..-1.jpg?resize=640%2C536\" alt=\"aplikasi convert pdf to word\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Tap-OPEN-atau-SEND-Enjoy-as..-1.jpg?w=800 800w, https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Tap-OPEN-atau-SEND-Enjoy-as..-1.jpg?resize=768%2C643 768w, https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Tap-OPEN-atau-SEND-Enjoy-as..-1.jpg?resize=740%2C620 740w, https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Tap-OPEN-atau-SEND-Enjoy-as..-1.jpg?resize=70%2C60 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" width=\"640\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px 10px; display: inline-block;\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Kira-kira begitu cara mengconvert PDF ke Word secara online, menggunakan software, ataupun lewat hp Android kamu, mudah bukan?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-weight: 400; margin: 24px 0px 14px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 29px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">#4 &ndash; Cara Mengubah PDF ke Word Menggunakan Microsoft&nbsp;Office</strong></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2360\" data-permalink=\"http://inewbiee.com/cara-convert-pdf-ke-word/cara-convert-pdf-to-word-online/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/cara-convert-pdf-to-word-online.jpeg?fit=690%2C300\" data-orig-size=\"690,300\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\" data-image-title=\"cara convert pdf to word online\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/cara-convert-pdf-to-word-online.jpeg?fit=320%2C190\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/cara-convert-pdf-to-word-online.jpeg?fit=640%2C278\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2360 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/cara-convert-pdf-to-word-online.jpeg?resize=640%2C278\" alt=\"cara convert pdf to word online\" width=\"640\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px 10px; display: inline-block;\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Cara mengubah PDF ke Word menggunakan microsoft office hanya bisa dilakukan kalau kamu memiliki software terbarunya MS Office, minimal versi 2013 keatas.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Mengapa? Karena sejak versi tersebutlah pihak Microsoft telah menambahkan fitur baru yang memungkinkan kita untuk membuka ataupun mengedit file PDF langsung di MS Word.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Dalam tutorial kali ini, Newbiee menggunakan microsoft word 2016, yuk simak cara-caranya.</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" open=\"\">\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 26px; margin-left: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Jalankan aplikasi Microsoft Word, kemudian cari dan pilih file yang akan diubah. Atau bisa juga klik kanan pada mouse, dan pilih open with &gt; Word.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2371\" data-permalink=\"http://inewbiee.com/cara-convert-pdf-ke-word/klik-kanan-open-with-word/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-kanan-open-with-word.jpg?fit=622%2C500\" data-orig-size=\"622,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\" data-image-title=\"Klik kanan &ndash; open with word\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-kanan-open-with-word.jpg?fit=320%2C190\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-kanan-open-with-word.jpg?fit=622%2C500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2371 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-kanan-open-with-word.jpg?resize=622%2C500\" alt=\"aplikasi pdf ke word\" width=\"622\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px 10px; display: inline-block;\" /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" open=\"\">\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 26px; margin-left: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Kemudian akan muncul notifikasi untuk mengubah PDF ke file editable Word, langsung di klik&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&ldquo;OK&rdquo;</strong>&nbsp;saja</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2372\" data-permalink=\"http://inewbiee.com/cara-convert-pdf-ke-word/klik-ok-pada-notifikasi-word/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-OK-pada-notifikasi-word.jpg?fit=800%2C316\" data-orig-size=\"800,316\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\" data-image-title=\"Klik OK pada notifikasi word\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-OK-pada-notifikasi-word.jpg?fit=320%2C190\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-OK-pada-notifikasi-word.jpg?fit=640%2C253\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2372 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-OK-pada-notifikasi-word.jpg?resize=640%2C253\" alt=\"cara ubah pdf ke word\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-OK-pada-notifikasi-word.jpg?w=800 800w, https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Klik-OK-pada-notifikasi-word.jpg?resize=768%2C303 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" width=\"640\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px 10px; display: inline-block;\" /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" open=\"\">\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 26px; margin-left: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Seletah itu, edit dokumen yang diperlukan.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2373\" data-permalink=\"http://inewbiee.com/cara-convert-pdf-ke-word/edit-file-yang-diperlukan/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Edit-file-yang-diperlukan.jpg?fit=800%2C330\" data-orig-size=\"800,330\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\" data-image-title=\"Edit file yang diperlukan\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Edit-file-yang-diperlukan.jpg?fit=320%2C190\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Edit-file-yang-diperlukan.jpg?fit=640%2C264\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2373 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Edit-file-yang-diperlukan.jpg?resize=640%2C264\" alt=\"aplikasi convert pdf ke word\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Edit-file-yang-diperlukan.jpg?w=800 800w, https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Edit-file-yang-diperlukan.jpg?resize=768%2C317 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" width=\"640\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px 10px; display: inline-block;\" /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" open=\"\">\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 26px; margin-left: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Nah, kalau sudah, langsung saja di-save dengan mengklik tombol file &gt; Save.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2374\" data-permalink=\"http://inewbiee.com/cara-convert-pdf-ke-word/kalau-ingin-save-klik-file-save/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Kalau-ingin-save-klik-file-Save.jpg?fit=800%2C530\" data-orig-size=\"800,530\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\" data-image-title=\"Kalau ingin save &ndash; klik file &ndash; Save\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Kalau-ingin-save-klik-file-Save.jpg?fit=320%2C190\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Kalau-ingin-save-klik-file-Save.jpg?fit=640%2C424\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2374 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Kalau-ingin-save-klik-file-Save.jpg?resize=640%2C424\" alt=\"cara mengedit pdf\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Kalau-ingin-save-klik-file-Save.jpg?w=800 800w, https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Kalau-ingin-save-klik-file-Save.jpg?resize=768%2C509 768w, https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Kalau-ingin-save-klik-file-Save.jpg?resize=300%2C200 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" width=\"640\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px 10px; display: inline-block;\" /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" open=\"\">\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 26px; margin-left: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Selanjutnya, pilih format file yang akan di-save di&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Save as Type,&nbsp;</strong>kemudian pilih PDF (*.pdf)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2375\" data-permalink=\"http://inewbiee.com/cara-convert-pdf-ke-word/pilih-save-as-type-dan-klik-pdf/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Pilih-save-as-type-dan-klik-PDF.jpg?fit=595%2C521\" data-orig-size=\"595,521\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\" data-image-title=\"Pilih save as type dan klik PDF\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Pilih-save-as-type-dan-klik-PDF.jpg?fit=320%2C190\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Pilih-save-as-type-dan-klik-PDF.jpg?fit=595%2C521\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2375 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Pilih-save-as-type-dan-klik-PDF.jpg?resize=595%2C521\" alt=\"cara edit file pdf\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Pilih-save-as-type-dan-klik-PDF.jpg?w=595 595w, https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Pilih-save-as-type-dan-klik-PDF.jpg?resize=70%2C60 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px\" width=\"595\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px 10px; display: inline-block;\" /></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" open=\"\">\r\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 26px; margin-left: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Ubah nama sesuai keinginan, intinya yang berbeda dengan nama PDF yang sebelumnya. Kemudian klik&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&ldquo;OK&rdquo;</strong>.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2376\" data-permalink=\"http://inewbiee.com/cara-convert-pdf-ke-word/ganti-nama-klik-save/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Ganti-nama-klik-save.jpg?fit=580%2C460\" data-orig-size=\"580,460\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\" data-image-title=\"Ganti nama &ndash; klik save\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Ganti-nama-klik-save.jpg?fit=320%2C190\" data-large-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Ganti-nama-klik-save.jpg?fit=580%2C460\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2376 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Ganti-nama-klik-save.jpg?resize=580%2C460\" alt=\"cara mengedit file pdf\" width=\"580\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px 10px; display: inline-block;\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Jreng-jreng, file pun telah selesai di&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">edit</em>&nbsp;dan siap untuk digunakan.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2377\" data-permalink=\"http://inewbiee.com/cara-convert-pdf-ke-word/selesai/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Selesai.jpg?fit=800%2C625\" data-orig-size=\"800,625\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\" data-image-title=\"Selesai\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Selesai.jpg?fit=320%2C190\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Selesai.jpg?fit=640%2C500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2377 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Selesai.jpg?resize=640%2C500\" alt=\"cara edit file pdf\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Selesai.jpg?w=800 800w, https://i1.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Selesai.jpg?resize=768%2C600 768w, https://i0.wp.com/inewbiee.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Selesai.jpg?resize=794%2C620 794w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" width=\"640\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px 10px; display: inline-block;\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Kamu bisa pilih deh salah satu cara yang paling praktis, mudah, dan cepat &nbsp;yang tentunya paling sesuai dengan kebutuhan kamu.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \" open=\"\">Sumber :&nbsp;http://inewbiee.com/cara-convert-pdf-ke-word/</p>', '', '', '0', 1);
